<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>관리자 로그인</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page-shell login-shell">
      <section class="login-card">
        <div class="login-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">ADMIN ACCESS</p>
          <h1>운영 화면 로그인</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">
            배포 환경에서는 관리자 키를 한 번 입력하면 쿠키로 인증을 유지합니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <% if (flashMessage) { %>
          <div class="flash flash-<%= flashLevel %>"><%= flashMessage %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form class="login-form" method="post" action="/admin/login">
          <input type="hidden" name="returnTo" value="<%= returnTo %>" />

          <label class="field">
            <span>관리자 키</span>
            <input type="password" name="adminKey" autocomplete="current-password" required />
          </label>

          <button type="submit" class="primary-button login-button">운영 화면 열기</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
